c: 6
v: 73
t: "And He it is Who created the heavens and the earth in truth. And the Day He will say: \"Be\", so it (i.e., the process of Resurrection) shall be. His Statement is the Truth. And for Him is the dominion — the Day, is blown in As-Soor. (He is the) Knower of the unseen and the seen. And He is All-Wise, All-Aware"